gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Suns 104, Nuggets 97
gameRecap.excerpt: The Suns defeated the Nuggets, 104-97. Kevin Durant led Phoenix with 30 points, along with season-highs in rebounds (13) and blocks (five), as Devin Booker added 17 points, five rebounds, and nine assists. Nikola Jokic led Denver with 22 points, nine rebounds, and 10 assists. Phoenix improves to 43-30 as the Nuggets move to 51-22. The Suns move to the 7 seed with the win.
